{"tid":1666291,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"賤賊就係暴徒","createTime":"2019-10-21T02:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T12:54:27.000Z","uid":48234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1a7f890f8597807e9b260de87ae2999e129e9ced","tid":1666291,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:33:50.000Z","msg":"催淚彈，戇膠彈，海綿彈，藍屍毒水亂鳩咁用<br />\n造成生態災難，有隻鴿食催淚彈，要由示威者去救<br />\n藍屍毒水噴清真寺，又係示威者幫手清潔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">禍就<span style=\"color: blue;\">賤賊</span>闖，屎就示威者執<br />\n仲好意思話示威者係暴徒，想分化香港人!<br />\n一班倒果為因嘅<span style=\"color: blue;\">賤賊</span>冚家剷!<br />\n解散<span style=\"color: blue;\">賤隊</span>!<br />\n光復香港，時代革命!</span></span>"},{"pid":"5fa5a9f1186116977b8875f31e30c636e05ca7ab","tid":1666291,"uid":268462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T02:47:22.000Z","msg":"對中資咁樣做先啱㗎嘛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666310</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c6c37ff5bfd515e81b0eb1d0d8cd586bc0a42eb0","tid":1666291,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"Fuck the police! 死差佬屌你老母!"},{"pid":"fcaa0a2901881f30df219d44455e4ee7c66c1be1","tid":1666291,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:08:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68015d654a3e28d1c334eb84bf27fecc573d836","tid":1666291,"uid":327740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15998065f0ff31e68c273d8bc28e1ad34a26efaf","tid":1666291,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:11:34.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"c154016a304d37ce54cad09fe8add07f26e8664f","tid":1666291,"uid":132056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:12:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天滅中共 全黨死清光</span></span>"},{"pid":"45aa62b88caa55b0f11006a0e10121fa375eb5a9","tid":1666291,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"1641b309237df386e488d766994802960e4b4f57","tid":1666291,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e68015d654a3e28d1c334eb84bf27fecc573d836","tid":1666291,"uid":327740,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:10:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T12:54:27.000Z","msg":"睇呢個post笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}